<title>USA: Equity Residential to purchase properties.</title>
<headline>Equity Residential to purchase properties.</headline>
<dateline>CHICAGO 1997-07-09</dateline>
<text>
<p>Equity Residential Properties Trust, a real estate investment trust, said Wednesday it entered an agreement with an affiliate of the Ameritech Corp Pension Trust to purchase 17 multifamily properties.</p>
<p>The properties consist of 5,105 units in 13 states.</p>
<p>In exchange, it said it will issue to Ameritech approximately 3,456,354 common shares and assume about $136 million in debt, for a total consideration of $292.4 million.</p>
<p>The company said the transaction is subject to due diligence and other conditions and approvals.</p>
<p>Equity Residential owns or has investments in 345 properties in 32 states.</p>
<p>((Reuters Chicago Newsdesk (312) 408-8787))</p>
